new EEI negative confirms Cc Forwarded by Leslie SmithHOUECT on PM Stephanie Piwetz PM To Brenna NRON Leslie CT cc Subject new EEI negative confirms Brenna Leslie and Team Just to let you know the counterparties we have an EEI agreement with and we send negative confirms to have the same look as if it was a regular confimation letter but without signature places For instance Reliant Energy Deal negative confirm looks just like a regular confirmation letter the number is in the upper right hand corner as well You all can just file the negative confirmations like usual and execute the Enron Confirmations that have two signatures Please call with any questions
